    <item>
      <title>OPEC+下个月可能需要解决石油产能难题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/opec-may-need-to-tackle-oil-capacity-conundrum-next-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OPEC+下个月召开会议时的主要问题是是否要在下半年继续削减石油供应。但它可能还需要解决产能的长期问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/opec-may-need-to-tackle-oil-capacity-conundrum-next-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 10:02:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
