      <title>交易员将美联储首次全面降息提前至 11 月，先于就业机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/traders-pull-forward-first-full-fed-rate-cut-to-november-ahead-of-jobs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券交易员提高了对美联储首次降息的预期，推动美国国债在重要的美国就业报告公布之前上涨，该报告将揭示经济状况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/traders-pull-forward-first-full-fed-rate-cut-to-november-ahead-of-jobs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
